# 🏗 Layered Architecture

```text
Client
   │
   ▼
Controller
   │
   ▼
Service
   │
   ▼
Repository
   │
   ▼
Database
```

---

# 🔄 Spring Boot Request Flow

```text
User Request
      │
      ▼
Controller
      │
      ▼
Service
      │
      ▼
Repository
      │
      ▼
Database
      │
      ▼
Response
```

---

# 🌍 Real-Life Example

```text
Hospital Management System

Patient
    │
    ▼
Reception (Controller)
    │
    ▼
Doctor (Service)
    │
    ▼
Medical Records (Repository)
    │
    ▼
Database
```

